msg:
Keep dialog open on long click of save button

To quickly add multiple notes, you can hold down the save button, which
clears the input field and save the reminder. Because this behaviour might
be confusing, it's disabled by default and can be enabled in the
preferences dialog.
name: icechen1/Notable

msg:
Add preference to set notification visibility

Notifications aren't shown on the lock screen, because the might contain
sensible information. But it's also handy to have the notes on the lock
screen while on a shopping tour and marking the bought goods. Hence, let
the user decide in the preferences dialog, what he wants.
name: icechen1/Notable

msg:
Use ScrollListener for current support library

Use RecyclerView.OnScrollListener instead of FloatingActionButton.Behavior for create activities in order to use current support library again: FloatingActionButton is hidden when scrolling down and shown when scrolling up.
The scrolling behavior for delete activities is unchanged and therefore still different: FloatingActionButton is hidden during scrolling and shown when scrolling stops.

Fixes: #36
name: SecUSo/privacy-friendly-shopping-list
